    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1937-08-17T22:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1937-08-17T22:00:00-05:00" n="702"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d702">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">834.01/39: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Paraguay</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Howard</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Asunción</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1937-08-17T23:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 17, 1937—11 p.m. [<hi rend="italic">a.m.?</hi>]</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 2:11 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>23. I have just been invited by the Under Secretary for Foreign Affairs to meet
                    this afternoon together with my colleagues Dr. Luis Argana Minister of Justice
                    and Public Instruction, and Acting Minister for Foreign Affairs pending arrival
                    tomorrow of Dr. Baez.<note n="6" xml:id="d702fn6">Cecilio Baez, Minister for
                        Foreign Affairs.</note> The Under Secretary states that it is not the
                    intention of this meeting to imply recognition of the new government which he
                    states is being requested through the Paraguayan Legations. While my acceptance
                    would undoubtedly be conducive to the creation of friendly feeling I shall make
                    no move pending instructions.</p>
                <p>I am trying to secure as much information as possible regarding the new
                    government and its personnel and expect to forward same later in the day.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Howard</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
